title: Sword Art Online: Progressive
description: “There’s no way to beat this game. The only difference is when and where you die…”One month has passed since Akihiko Kayaba’s deadly game began, and the body count continues to rise. Two thousand players are already dead.Kirito and Asuna are two very different people, but they both desire to fight alone.
